content: <xml>   <records>        <record>       <contributors>         <authors>           <author>Morton, Timothy</author>         </authors>       </contributors>       <titles>         <title>Dartmouth Stellar Evolution Grids</title>         <secondary-title/>       </titles>       <doi>10.5281/zenodo.15843</doi>       <pages/>       <volume/>       <number>doi</number>       <dates>         <year>2015</year>         <pub-dates>           <date>2015-03-04</date>         </pub-dates>       </dates>       <abstract><p>Dartmouth stellar model grids, used by the &#39;isochrones&#39; python package (github.com/timothydmorton/isochrones).&nbsp; Update from previous grids; these now include WISE bands, ages &lt; 1Gyr, and have coarser Fe/H sampling.</p></abstract>     </record>      </records> </xml>
